data.description: GORGEOUSLY CHARMING BRICK BEAUTY IN THE DESIRABLE FOREST PARK SUBDIVISION WITH TREE LINED STREETS CENTRALLY LOCATED NEAR MERCY ONE! The character not only shines on the outside but follows suite on the inside with the stunning coffered ceilings in both the kitchen and dining room along with stunning hardwood floors accents. Arched doorways start at the front door entryway and carry through from the living room to the dining room/kitchen area. Kitchen offers a snack bar, great cabinetry and countertop space as well as a window overlooking the rear yard. New French doors to the deck with built-in seating, shaded by nature's beauty - room to kick back and relax. Huge master suite upstairs complete with walk-in closet, full bath, and bonus space perfect for a reading nook, office or toy room. If you need more space, head downstairs for an oversized storage room, laundry room with 1/2 bath, & bonus space currently used as an in-home gym. It's time to make this rare gem your new home today!
